# How to delete an organisation

- Navigate to the All Organisations tab on the left-hand sidebar.
- Browse the list or use the "Search by organisation name" search bar to find the specific company you wish to remove.
- Click on the Name of the organization (e.g. "A Company") to open its details page.

<img src="/images/all_org_list.png">

- On the organization's details page, verify you are viewing the correct entity by checking the location details.
- Scroll down to the very bottom of the page, below the "IPs" section.
- Click the red delete organisation button.

<img src="/images/all_orgs_delete_org.png">

<img src="/images/delete_org_confirmation.png">

Look for a banner at the top of the screen displaying the message: "Organisation has been removed".
You can search for the organization name again to ensure it no longer appears in the list.

<img src="/images/orgs_removed.png">
